sentences: Pramod Kharel (Nepali: प्रमोद खरेल; born 6 November 1979) is a Nepalese singer.
He has recorded more than 2000 songs of different genres.
He is a coach in The Voice of Nepal Season 1 (2018), 2 (2019) & 3 (2020-2021).
